hush-vani-weights

This crate redistributes the model weights of "Hush" by Weya AI:

    https://huggingface.co/weya-ai/hush

The weights (data/weights.bin, data/weights.txt) are a repackaging of the ONNX
bundle published there, converted to a flat little-endian f32 arena. No weight
values are modified; only the container format differs.

